                  </persName> was <hi rend="italic">again</hi> indicted<rs id="t18450707-1548-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18450707-1548-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18450707-1548-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing 1 yard of printed cotton, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 108 shirt-buttons, 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. and half a yard of tweed, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18450707-name-507" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450707-name-507" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450707-name-507" type="surname" value="ROBINSON"></interp>
